{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"43ea2382e5","title":"几个反革命分子的内心世界","origin":"湖北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f4be3d6d28","index":0,"year":1963,"month":8,"day":13,"articleId":"43ea2382e5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0b21b68f9c","type":"title","text":"几个反革命分子的内心世界","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"51b0b15bb9","type":"subtitle","text":"一个右派分子的两则日记","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"d27167a5df","type":"paragraph","text":"今年二月，武汉市人民银行汉阳办事处在检查卫生时，发现了右派分子李志聪（已摘帽子）的几篇日记。兹摘录其中的两篇如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"05cba80229","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年十一月十二日：“我绝不向宗派主义和教条主义者投降，我要沉默地抗议到底。在他们既定了的路线下，再永不做那为党牺牲的一切美梦了。在宗派主义和唯成分论者的统治下，任何幻想都是白费的……。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"8ae47c50f8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年十二月十四日：“不畏强权，不屈服于强权，不阿谀强者，这是我过去的指导思想，也是将来的指导思想，我不迷信任何人，也不把权威当作图腾膜拜。但是为了自己要去争取的生活，有时不得不考虑方式，作战略上的退却，正象C所说的，将拳头收回来是为了打出去更有力。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"fc0463a5a6","type":"subtitle","text":"一个反革命的“汇报”材料","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"8cba0076f4","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年十二月至一九六三年四月，武汉市江汉分局大夹街派出所，接连收到了反革命分子王道义的几份“汇报”材料。这个反革命分子以写汇报材料为名，猖狂地向我进攻。但是管段民警却没有看出来，还认为他表现“不错”。下面录其两段：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"def7cbf624","type":"appellation","text":"“最近我出来向监改小组报告，想法是：处分就处分，这种日子没有什么过头，我在着急的时候，只是在关心各方面演变的趋势，是否适合我的理想。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"af7d1b248e","type":"paragraph","text":"“生活在困难中……要活着就要做事，不做事就不要活着，我虽不致于死，但也不存在逃避死，我想只要我不死，总有一天我是可以为人的。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"d5b669975d","type":"subtitle","text":"反动分子刘圣时的四首诗","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"d1cad657fd","type":"appellation","text":"反动分子刘圣时写了一本反动诗集，录其四首如后：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"164db75a7b","type":"paragraph","text":"一、送石岚风回潜江。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"715c2cccf4","type":"paragraph","text":"一自丁酉狂飚后，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"d70a1ebaa6","type":"paragraph","text":"相知零落有几人。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"9f9b2dd4bc","type":"paragraph","text":"永生长存勾践恨，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"46d422f2a4","type":"paragraph","text":"壮逝堪掉专诸魂。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"de7e39567c","type":"paragraph","text":"万里江山凭指点，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"029502f10c","type":"paragraph","text":"八千风云任酌斟。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"eae22a13f8","type":"paragraph","text":"天下蛟鸷看颜色，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"387462c5e6","type":"paragraph","text":"敢以太阿分天庭。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"6481ddb100","type":"paragraph","text":"（编者注：这个反动分子，在一九五七年反右派时，因恶毒地攻击我党，曾受过批判。这首诗头两句的意思是：自一九五七年（丁酉年）那次狂风暴雨般的斗争以后，自己就感到很孤单寂寞，但是他并不甘心，所以第三、四两句就说：要象勾践那样永远记住仇恨，要学习刺杀吴王僚的专诸，一有机会就进行暗杀、破坏活动。最后四句的意思大概是：要扩大反革命活动，以便时机到来时用“太阿”这样的宝剑劈开“天庭”，即实现反革命复辟。）","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"9a3ff40dcc","type":"paragraph","text":"二、寄王光容一首。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"32eb5a6842","type":"paragraph","text":"愁风愁雨愁满城，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"8ef2722cdb","type":"paragraph","text":"惨雾暮云秋更深。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"01d3aa49e9","type":"paragraph","text":"千百片舌论时局，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"9c6b85a5b4","type":"paragraph","text":"一二春秋定浮沉。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"12349b13c3","type":"paragraph","text":"尚晋清谈非甘愿，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"dd38bfc182","type":"paragraph","text":"崇汉博锥有忌心。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"f19437bb31","type":"paragraph","text":"留得醉活录后世，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"bc0c895260","type":"paragraph","text":"敢把热血洒典坟。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"0cdbb35551","type":"paragraph","text":"（编者注：这首诗的意思是：他很苦闷。许多人都在谈论局势，大概一、两年以后就可以见分晓了。他现在只是象魏晋南北朝时的士大夫一样地“清谈”，其实并非心甘情愿。他实在是想学刺杀秦始皇的张良，干一下反革命的暗杀活动，可是又害怕。所以只是作点诗，以便反革命复辟以后，得以流传后世。）","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"cff061a8bf","type":"paragraph","text":"三、招魂。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"a2b107c2e2","type":"paragraph","text":"一麻榆槐林立的小岛，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"f18bb58dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"方是我们充满想象的乐园。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"03bc4e28a3","type":"paragraph","text":"这小岛是大陆的前线，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"2a526d79a1","type":"paragraph","text":"故乡、亲人住在大陆里，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"ccc83ae603","type":"paragraph","text":"对这些侨居海外的游子，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"769de10b41","type":"paragraph","text":"早已频频问讯，繁繁地致着信息。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"e37f24bc27","type":"paragraph","text":"……好容易粉碎了那魔鬼的羁绊，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"c492966308","type":"paragraph","text":"带领了思乡的人们远走，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"4ca27990ac","type":"paragraph","text":"只要顺风的狂飚，倾刻归来，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"8906168698","type":"paragraph","text":"这家园的院楼。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"4e7ee5431c","type":"paragraph","text":"归来吧！海国的游魂，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"b792d7d6e8","type":"paragraph","text":"归来吧！孤岛的幽灵，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"27eb5ed397","type":"paragraph","text":"这里的第一坯土","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"8c0ee4ea59","type":"paragraph","text":"都渗透着汗浇血淋……。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"de476e05ca","type":"paragraph","text":"四、洗劫。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"892d457ebd","type":"paragraph","text":"上帝降临了遍地疮痍的人间，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"d8b62afb16","type":"paragraph","text":"咀里嗫诺着天经的谒语：","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"3392cf5a06","type":"paragraph","text":"“我的宇下的儿女们！","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"58d9ceb409","type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶已经深深地插入了你们的心灵，","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"ff007e60a1","type":"paragraph","text":"……天国已没有你们卑劣的席位，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"63b0f1994b","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的善、恶、勇、智都是虚伪的定义。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"1c5568a493","type":"paragraph","text":"……病人膏盲无法可治，","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"9fbe680a78","type":"paragraph","text":"……等待毁灭……。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"809df735c1","type":"paragraph","text":"乌云已待命从四方笼罩，","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"dbfaca9cf4","type":"paragraph","text":"狂风已鼓起饱满的口袋，","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"ccc62abdd2","type":"paragraph","text":"骤雨将倾出复盆的浊流，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"35aa50392b","type":"paragraph","text":"大地已裂开漆黑的大口，","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"2ff548ead3","type":"paragraph","text":"天崩地裂，山倾海催，","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"238fa05883","type":"paragraph","text":"……污秽、黑暗、腐朽、丑恶已布满地域，","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"ae1879a885","type":"paragraph","text":"……我们要在那疯狂的淫乐中审讯，","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"db9bfac99f","type":"paragraph","text":"审讯那些无神论者，那些自以为是、以人定胜天的","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"ce8c7ae194","type":"paragraph","text":"谎言作幌的骗子，","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"0766892838","type":"paragraph","text":"我们将亲见“你”们在无可挽的浩劫中，","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"855aa07e6e","type":"paragraph","text":"先失去头颅，先让你们亲见自己的亲人，妻女悲痛，","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"e896dfbafd","type":"paragraph","text":"供人玩弄，","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"1b1cc0e140","type":"paragraph","text":"把邪恶集于一身，报复惩罚一身……。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"249f11fd72","type":"subtitle","text":"二个五类分子的阴谋","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"2f5e46e2ac","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉市第二砖瓦厂右派分子李世英（已摘帽）五月二十八日对另一个未摘帽子的右派分子熊茂辉说：“你的性格要放好一点，为了保存自己，有事就不要放在表面上。要接受改造，积极老实，内心不投降。不这样是不成的，刀把子掌握在他们手上。我就是如此，虽摘了帽子，并没有心服，内心没有投降。”","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"762e8e0e6b","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉市江汉区兴叶里反革命分子彭世明，今年三月对一个投机倒把分子刘德珊说：“一个人心要毒些，无毒不成丈夫，没有毒气那是一个人！”又说：“如果反了面，老子一刀一个，杀得共产党一个不留！我叔父（反革命，已镇压）是一个英雄，我要向他学习！”","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"},{"id":"1c8483c596","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自武汉市公安局“情况简报”第六十三期）","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5"}],"page":{"id":"ba74366c39","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"43ea2382e5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}